So I was nominated to do this 10 facts about me thing(?) by @gravityy_z and I'm not keen on it, but whatever, here goes.
•I'm 27 years old going on 28 here in a few more days(October 7th(send me something (I'm lonely 😂)))
•I live alone here in Virginia and I'm currently getting my house remodeled (should see the bathroom. It's paradise).
•I spent 6 years of my life as a United States Marine with the MOSs' of 7011 and a 3112.
•This picture was taken when I was stationed in Japan. It took place during Valentine's day. I didn't have a date, but the place I was invited to was a "dress to impress" place, so I wore what I had(the suit was what I wore to my highschool prom😂)
•I got into gaming at a very young age, but I didn't start the competitive scene until late Halo 2. My team and I(John, Stephen, Travis) did Halo 3 competitively and we ended up in 47th out of thousands of teams. Top 50 is impressive in my eyes. When Bungie gave Halo over to 343 I was kinda disappointed. Then Destiny came into the picture and here I am now.
•I love to travel. I've been all over the US, I've been to Japan, Australia, Philippines, Thailand, Italy, and other places. I'm planning a trip to Vegas and Greece soon.
•I love to read and write. I've never published anything, but I do have a few fantasy-related stories that I'm proud of.
•I'm currently a bartender and it's a fun job. I enjoy it.
•Sometimes I can be a little too hype(if you haven't watched my streams/posts😂). I just like to see others laugh and to be happy.
•Team Enigma would not have happened if I didn't meet @chuchigaming or @lonexwolflegend in a Destiny Facebook community group. Thank you Wolf for giving me the opportunity to show you my potential and thank you Chuchi for sticking around and remaining loyal through all the bumps.🌹

caption.text:
Hey Noobz this is Don’t Blink’tober, the videogame we are drawing for the inktober challenge.
This year I m doing the #inktober2019 challenge with my illustrator/gamer friendz @zed.bamba & @marlene_c.kim
Just like #inktober , each day of the month is linked to a word from the official @jakeparker  inktober prompt list, but we wrote a game scenario from it.
Follow our progress on proto-livestreaming in this meta game. 
Featuring : openworld exploration, mesmerizing game design, fuckedup end bosses, mindblowing puzzles, crazy loot, 360 no scope headshots, immersive graphics and the meta bonus : original sound track composed by the gameboy himself :  @matt.g.verona
See you tomorrow for the launch of this adventure .
.
.
.
#drawing #videogames #animation #illustration #illustratoroninstagram #dessin #jeuxvideo
.
.
.
. 
Salut les twittos voici Don’t Blink’tober, le jeu vidéo dessiné pour inktober.
Cette année, je ferai le défi Inktober en compagnie des dessinatrices/gameuses @zed.bamba et @marlene_c.kim. 
Comme pour Inktober, chaque jour du mois d’octobre est lié à un mot de la liste officielle, mais nous avons écrit un scénario de jeu vidéo à partir de cette fameuse liste.
Suivez en proto-livestreaming notre évolution dans les différents stages de ce jeu !
Au programme :  explo openworld, game design renversant, boss de fin de niveaux completements pétés, puzzles machiavéliques, loot de dingue, headshots 360 no scope, simulation immersive VR sur ton telephone et le meta bonus : des vrais morceaux de bande son par notre compositeur sur gameboy @matt.g.verona
Rdv demain sur instagram pour le début de nos aventures

No.156 Quilava  マグマラシ

preview_comments.text: Un gran avance el que ha hecho Nintendo, aunque me parece que en este tipo de cosas sigue estando bastante anticuada y por detrás de los otros sistemas

caption.text: ... y ese motivo es poder usar las dos consolas como si fuera una. Al contrario que Nintendo 3DS, donde teníamos que eliminar y borrar los datos de una, para usar la otra, con la Cuenta Nintendo, no pasa. Podemos usar nuestra cuenta en Switch y Switch Lite, al mismo tiempo, compartiendo online, juegos digitales y el guardado de partidas en la nube. Solo una pega; la consola secundaria, necesita conexión a internet permanente, para poder jugar. Pero, he aquí la jugada; convertir en consola principal nuestra Lite, y como secundaria, la Switch original. Con este “setup” mi Switch original se queda en casa, con conexión permanente, y conectada a la TV, y la Lite la uso exclusivamente como portátil, y así poder jugar, sin necesitar conexión. Con el guardado en la nube, puedo descargar todas mis partidas y seguir jugando. Obviamente, tener los dos sistemas no es necesario. Pero si compartimos esta afición, tener ambas,  puede ser una opción interésante, y disfrutar de las bondades de ambos sistemas. Por el momento, estoy llevándome la Switch Lite a todos lados, cuando antes, era más reservado, y me daba “cosa” llevármela según donde. En breves me voy de viaje y podré probarla a fondo. Espero haber arrojado algo de luz a vuestras dudas! #nintendoswitch #nintendoswitchlite #nintendo #brummelgames #gamer #videogames #nin10do #nintendoswitch #retrogamer #gamerroom #switch #nintendo3ds

caption.text:
Zelda AU centering around Demise’s Curse!

There was a huge war centuries ago, in which the corrupted Ganon threatened to destroy the world. The battle caused massive repercussions in which most people died.

Now they are all being reborn.

All memories of past lives are sealed until a certain, specific trigger awakens them. Once a person has been awoken, they are vulnerable to be corrupted by the malice, Demise’s Curse.
Devastated by their assigned fate, they start to turn into creatures full of nothing but hatred.

Send me some asks @ demisescurse on Tumblr :)

История Орды. Начало.
Жила на планете Аргус раса эредаров (внезапное начало истории орды, да?).И правил этой расой совет экзархов в лице трёх деятелей, таких как Архимонд, Кил’Джеден и Велен.

Правили они мудро и было у них всё хорошо, но до одного момента. Дело в том, что Саргерас устал самолично управлять большим количеством демонов (они же все разномастные, не особо покорные и не особо умные) и понял, что ему нужны полководцы. Тут то история Саргераса и эредаров пересекается, ибо поехавший титан обратил внимание на высокоцивилизованную расу.

Явившись к экзархам в лице сущности светлой и сияющей, он сделал им предложение знаний, силы, просветления и много другого. Архимонд и Кил’Джеден с радостью приняли его предложение, однако Велена терзали смутные сомнения. Особенно после того, как ему (Велену) явилось видение (ах да, забыл сказать, Велен пророк) того, что произойдёт с его народом, если они примут предложение Саргераса (красная кожа, злые морды, короче трэш и угар). Продолжение этой истории  можете прочитать в нашей группе ВКонтакте
